{"tid":724022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(這些機會是屬於我的) 世界盃之旅 - 直擊決賽之路","createTime":"2018-06-30T16:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T13:29:31.000Z","uid":118434,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba4618b1ca7edea030e17d8498b8b193b456694","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"去咗俄羅斯睇世界盃，會睇六場波包括西班牙對俄羅斯，瑞典對瑞士，索契場八強，兩場四強以及決賽！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想用呢個post紀錄一吓旅程嘅點滴，同時希望各位熟悉俄羅斯嘅巴打絲打可以分享一吓有咩好玩好食。我打字好慢，可能會update得比較慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，今日剛到埗，去相<br />\n<br />\n指定動作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/004819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F004819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=11514bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄航客機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/004834_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F004834_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5b8006e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未起飛已經有乘客發生爭執，fuck嚟fuck去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/004912_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F004912_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=98739680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄航空姐<br />\n理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/004934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F004934_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1c93f018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/005018_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F005018_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86625e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n望到背脊都feel到啲肉地，不了<br />\n<br />\n一落機法國對阿根廷已經開緊波，排咗好耐先過到關，過完關喺機場睇埋下半場先走，有大家熟悉嘅俄文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見證麥巴比屈機同美斯登機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/france.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/005140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F005140_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a445a96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為手持波飛，可以免費搭airport express出市區，講到呢度先，未完待續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/005706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F005706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=19cbe94a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"915a5ad1beecdafb14265cdad4fc64e19ab09c97","tid":724022,"uid":165160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"152673e548209539bddc993da8c375838ad1258c","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2d2d11b0cb89092687c605f2a11213a6f953fc","tid":724022,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f1518184bd870369cdd0fce91223e1d829d1b1cf","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T22:18:20.000Z","msg":"呢幾日太攰了，無心機update，而家繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到市中心，啲地鐵站真係好靚，又好深入地底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/061652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F061652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=21d963f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheck in 完後喺附近搵咗間餐廳睇烏拉圭對葡萄牙，見證C朗陪同美斯一齊登機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/061720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F061720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bcda2000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1 完"},{"pid":"a819d5f832eb0b9d381baa2f6eaba3be43be2e3b","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T22:42:39.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n<br />\n第二朝去咗KFC食個早餐，好大份好飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/061908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F061908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=14b53ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去咗都幾出名嘅Tretyakov Gallery睇吓畫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/062153_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F062153_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b9bc7d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後重頭戲來了，入場睇西班牙對俄羅斯！可能因為梅德韋傑夫都有入場睇，所以安檢超嚴，摸勻全身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/062416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F062416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2e4f91dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/062412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F062412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=38f3dfdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以坐到八萬人嘅盧日尼基球場，我坐較正中嘅位，喺media隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/062534_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F062534_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fb004fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條match day scarf遲少少都賣晒呀，好彩買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/spain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/062622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F062622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8eefb95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開波！場波睇電視就應該有啲悶，但現場氣氛真係超級超級正！喺莫斯科最大個球場踢，全場近八萬人我諗超過九成都係撐俄羅斯，呢個體驗真係一世難忘！仲要第一場已經有埋加時同十二碼睇，真係值回票價！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063059_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063059_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f2a108c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063350_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063350_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fefa1f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完場了，俄羅斯晉級，現場氣氛好到不得了，相反西班牙的fans <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2ad748de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少少花絮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063432_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063432_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8bd9e824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063435_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7e2c1180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45e8c38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5a977a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n離開球場轉去Fan Fest睇下一場克羅地亞對丹麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/denmark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=55c81142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰度有間好大嘅Fan Store<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063536_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063536_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=da7650d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好大嘅場地，可以至少容納幾萬人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063554_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a15f613c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去搭免費通宵列車前往聖彼得堡繼續旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=53afa83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同房有兩個南亞裔，好彩佢哋好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/063744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F063744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8e410824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 2 完"},{"pid":"6334f407f21cf19e221aee20298ad61cac899c01","tid":724022,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"我都會去睇四強同決賽<br />\n不過後日先出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dded5ee104afd7b9e561a1a4fd18e40d9975c060","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"條頸巾喺邊度買 幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83203f0631114af319cd5049419509455cc3389","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dded5ee104afd7b9e561a1a4fd18e40d9975c060","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"條頸巾喺邊度買 幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"球場裏面買，RUB 2000"},{"pid":"88bc5fa77edd36bdfce132c0ed30687dadd7a7d2","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83203f0631114af319cd5049419509455cc3389","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dded5ee104afd7b9e561a1a4fd18e40d9975c060","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"條頸巾喺邊度買 幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"球場裏面買，RUB 2000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會有俄文野買"},{"pid":"3ac071c43a30f53b6f02c2ef0a631fa08f650bf1","tid":724022,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"食物影多點。<br />\n<br />\nnice"},{"pid":"85757222c8fbe68f595549661a64f9ff8b3ebb0b","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88bc5fa77edd36bdfce132c0ed30687dadd7a7d2","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d83203f0631114af319cd5049419509455cc3389","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dded5ee104afd7b9e561a1a4fd18e40d9975c060","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"條頸巾喺邊度買 幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"球場裏面買，RUB 2000"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會有俄文野買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T21:43:27.000Z","msg":"好似大部份都係英文"},{"pid":"b002485d6d599cb72b9ca7ae59da9b075b5666ca","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T22:12:54.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n<br />\n落火車後食咗個幾豐富嘅lunch，但呢度只係廿幾蚊港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/055659_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F055659_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3e51e227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後Check in 遇到啲問題，好彩最後都搞得掂，跟住去聖彼得堡嘅Fan Fest睇巴西對墨西哥，隔離就係著名嘅地標Church of the Savior on Spilled Blood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/055903_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F055903_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b3dbf06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個Fan Fest比莫斯科細好多，但都應該可以容納過萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/060009_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F060009_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8247e896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完場，失落的墨西哥Fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/brazil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/mexico.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/060116_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F060116_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bce0ff2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本想睇埋比利時對日本，但又凍又大雨，大雨到係香港紅色暴雨嗰隻，連搵間有波睇嘅餐廳都有困難，最後求其買個杯麵返酒店食算，一路食一路睇住日本光榮出局<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過估唔到呢個俄國杯麵又幾好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/06/060741_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F06%2F060741_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4840ab41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 3 完"},{"pid":"b9740556d0109db4619d41f417ee483d4a0849b6","tid":724022,"uid":31196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T22:33:25.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29380ba087d38eab48da4b756d569f6407314af","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85757222c8fbe68f595549661a64f9ff8b3ebb0b","tid":724022,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88bc5fa77edd36bdfce132c0ed30687dadd7a7d2","tid":724022,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislik